{"tid":2379951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【 達標！！！ 已籌得 1 月份預計開支 $1,500 萬元！】","createTime":"2021-01-25T14:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T14:17:29.000Z","uid":319380,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2625e8677c94684e633cf632c0160f7e2eab7094","tid":2379951,"uid":319380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"感謝11000名捐款人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基金上周三公佈 12 月份財務簡報，顯示可動用結餘為 $181 萬，估計不足以應付本月預計開支 $1,500 萬，並呼籲香港人踴躍捐款，令基金可繼續支援工作。<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家迅速反應及慷慨支持！短短 6 日內，基金已籌得超過 $1,150 萬，連同上月可動用結餘及 1 月初所得捐款，已超過 $1,500 萬目標！基金衷心感謝由 1 月初至今超過 11,000 捐款人的支持！<br />\n<br />\n為避免基金戶口持有龐大存款，懇請大家持續留意基金之公佈，如水一般靈活捐款。我們將於稍後公佈 1 月份工作報告及 2 月份預計開支，請屆時按基金所需再捐款支持。<br />\n<br />\n基金亦希望大家可登記月捐，協助基金更好地制訂預算。目前，已有超過 1,500 位支持者登記月捐，每月月捐金額約 $63 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n在這次募捐過程中，不少商鋪慷慨捐款並協助轉發消息，基金衷心感謝這些店鋪！我們稍後將貼出商店名單。<br />\n<br />\n基金再次感謝大家的支持及捐助！沒有你們，基金無法繼續支援反送中運動的在囚／還押者、被告、被捕者及傷者。我們會繼續謹守崗位。謝謝大家！<br />\n<br />\n（※ 基金實際收支數字以基金核數後財務報告為準）<br />\n-------------------<br />\n☎️ 申請熱線：9845 6641 個人資料，絕對保密<br />\n💰 捐款： <a href=\"https://donate.612fund.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdonate.612fund.hk&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=3d077f70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://donate.612fund.hk</a><br />\n🖥 FB： 612人道支援基金 612 Humanitarian Relief Fund<br />\n📷 IG： <a href=\"http://instagram.com/612fund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2F612fund&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=917eb736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/612fund</a><br />\n📱 TG： <a href=\"http://t.me/ReliefFund612_Update\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FReliefFund612_Update&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=6549c512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ReliefFund612_Update</a><br />\n📣 MeWe： <a href=\"http://mewe.com/p/612fund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fp%2F612fund&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=9375e4db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mewe.com/p/612fund</a>"},{"pid":"9e6a780ba2b001e406ac47df8b14e63a735eaf5f","tid":2379951,"uid":38953,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:08:42.000Z","msg":"平均一人捐咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954e0b86dbdbb7ccdf97ff9b6eaab740ab8d6b8b","tid":2379951,"uid":227788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:09:54.000Z","msg":"D舖唔執偷笑<br />\n仲肯損錢"},{"pid":"40d7972dd0e8afdbfb8ca166e662c19817e0d776","tid":2379951,"uid":319380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T14:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}